{"lastModified":1771253279155,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nIntroducing Eros, our stunning brand new addition to the fleet, a magnificent 4-cabin sailing yacht, the Bavaria Cruiser 46. Freshly built in 2024, Eros is docked in Alimos Marina, Greece.\n\nAccommodating up to 8 guests in four comfortable double cabins, Eros ensures a peaceful night’s sleep with pillows and blankets included in the package.\n\nWith three toilets and a shower onboard, Eros prioritizes your comfort and convenience throughout your journey.\n\nEquipped with a rolling mainsail, solar panels, bimini, and bow thruster, Eros guarantees a smooth sailing experience with modern amenities. Stay cozy with the brand new heating and air conditioning while enjoying your favorite tunes on the audio system with both inside and outside speakers.\n\nIn the fully-equipped galley, whip up gourmet meals with ease using the oven, cooker, sink, and kitchen utensils provided.","blueprint":{"name":"EROS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a431d7d0-37df-11f0-bca4-99c5a58e96f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a44d2800-37df-11f0-a3a4-7113f2dafe15/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a435f680-37df-11f0-a3a4-7113f2dafe15/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a4305130-37df-11f0-bca4-99c5a58e96f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a432c230-37df-11f0-bca4-99c5a58e96f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a44eaea0-37df-11f0-bca4-99c5a58e96f2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::21232e30-37d9-11f0-a9fd-adef43487e5f::assets::a4252da0-37df-11f0-bca4-99c5a58e96f2/{imageVa